<li>Translation of <i><a href="/wiki/Roman_de_la_Rose" title="Roman de la Rose">Roman de la Rose</a></i>, possibly extant as <i><a href="/wiki/The_Romance_of_the_Rose" title="The Romance of the Rose" class="mw-redirect">The Romance of the Rose</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Book_of_the_Duchess" title="The Book of the Duchess">The Book of the Duchess</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_House_of_Fame" title="The House of Fame">The House of Fame</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Anelida_and_Arcite" title="Anelida and Arcite">Anelida and Arcite</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Parlement_of_Foules" title="Parlement of Foules">Parlement of Foules</a></i></li>
<li>Translation of <a href="/wiki/Anicius_Manlius_Severinus_Boethius" title="Anicius Manlius Severinus Boethius">Boethius</a>' <i><a href="/wiki/Consolation_of_Philosophy" title="Consolation of Philosophy">Consolation of Philosophy</a></i> as <i><a href="/wiki/Boece_(Chaucer)" title="Boece (Chaucer)">Boece</a></i></li>
