</ul>
<p><a name="Short_poems" id="Short_poems"></a></p>
<h4><span class="mw-headline">Short poems</span></h4>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Balade_to_Rosemounde.jpg" class="image" title="To Rosemounde"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d6/Balade_to_Rosemounde.jpg/180px-Balade_to_Rosemounde.jpg" width="180" height="302" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
